Sanuki no Miyatsuko.

15
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:36,700
One day he noticed a light shining
from inside a bamboo stalk...

16
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:40,559
Curious the bamboo
cutter approached it.

17
00:01:43,649 --> 00:01:47,700
As he approached it, the light
flowed into the ground...

18
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:51,045
