seen before.

19
00:01:51,145 --> 00:01:53,000
What is this?

20
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:57,200
Bamboo shoot sprouting so early?
Even before the plums?

21
00:02:04,375 --> 00:02:06,300
What is this?

22
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,085
Have mercy on me!

23
00:02:27,565 --> 00:02:28,858
Hello...

24
00:02:29,316 --> 00:02:34,000
May I ask please, who might
you be, my lady?

25
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:07,104
Oh my! She is such a
beautiful little princess!

26
00:03:07,438 --> 00:03:12,526
It's a miracle! This must be a blessing
from Heaven, I'm sure of it!

27
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,955
You're back early.
Something wrong?

28
00:04:15,673 --> 00:04:17,758
Ah! What a beautiful
little doll!

29
