No quiet, you'll wake her.
She's sleeping.

30
00:04:20,261 --> 00:04:21,804
Ah!
Shh. Shh.

31
00:04:27,101 --> 00:04:28,936
She just appeared
to me in the grove.

32
00:04:29,061 --> 00:04:30,187
