a perfect little princess.

37
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:47,204
No no no! Don't be silly, there is
more to raising a child than you think.

38
00:04:47,663 --> 00:04:48,747
Right?

39
00:04:54,545 --> 00:04:56,300
