02:06:59,487 --> 02:07:03,500
* Lifetimes come and go in turn *
Princess! Princess!

1229
02:07:03,600 --> 02:07:07,621
* Over and over a life revives *
Princess!

1230
02:07:08,580 --> 02:07:09,956


1231
02:07:10,000 --> 02:07:17,000
* Over and over a life renews *

1232
02:07:19,215 --> 02:07:21,968
Princess! Don't leave us!

1233
02:07:22,427 --> 02:07:23,637
Not yet!

1234
02:07:24,262 --> 02:07:25,639
Please, not yet.

1235
02:07:26,931 --> 02:07:28,933
Once I dawn this robe...

1236
02:07:29,267 --> 02:07:32,979
I will forget everything I know
and love about this land.

1237
02:07:33,355 --> 02:07:35,900
So please just for a moment.

1238
02:07:38,276 --> 02:07:39,900
Princess!
Daughter!

1239
02:07:48,453 --> 02:07:49,496
Please!

1240
02:07:49,621 --> 02:07:53,193
Take us with you!
Take us with you!

1241
02:07:53,291 --> 02:07:56,800
Forgive me, Momma and Poppa!
Please forgive me!

1242
02:07:57,128 --> 02:07:59,172
Now now, let us go.

1243
02:07:59,297 --> 02:08:02,342
This heavy heart will no longer trouble you
in the City of the Moon...

1244
02:08:02,467 --> 02:08:07,347
And the memory of this impure Earth,
will lift from your mind forever.

1245
02:08:07,472 --> 02:08:08,848
It's not impure!

1246
02:08:11,810 --> 02:08:14,900
There is grief and sorrow here...

1247
02:08:15,700 --> 02:08:17,500
There is also joy and happiness!

1248
02:08:17,600 --> 02:08:22,000
All who live on this earth,
experience them in different shades.

1249
02:08:20,485 --> 02:08:22,028

1250
02:08:22,320 --> 02:08:24,197
All feel compassion.

1251
02:08:27,409 --> 02:08:28,702
Princess!

1252
02:08:44,700 --> 02:08:46,200
Princess!

1253
02:09:05,400 --> 02:09:06,600
Princess!

